327
00:14:37,540 --> 00:14:39,070
Chen Lei!

328
00:14:39,110 --> 00:14:40,860
Huan'er!

329
00:14:41,190 --> 00:14:42,190
Lina!

330
00:14:42,710 --> 00:14:43,430
Lina!

331
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:45,430
- Mom! Mom!
- Lina!

332
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:46,500
Mom!

333
00:14:47,310 --> 00:14:48,590
Why did you come back?

334
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:50,070
