335
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:51,310
Get your filthy hands off me!

336
00:14:51,310 --> 00:14:51,950
I tell you...

337
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:52,860
Take this!

338
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:55,740
You two are too much!

339
00:14:55,740 --> 00:14:56,990
You two scared me a lot.

340
00:14:56,990 --> 00:14:57,830
What is this?

341
00:14:57,830 --> 00:14:58,470
Look!

342
00:15:01,950 --> 00:15:03,830
Why don't you give me a banner?

343
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:04,640
Oh, right, Dad!

344
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:06,600
