- Sit down!

346
00:15:07,590 --> 00:15:09,950
You two bully me.

347
00:15:09,950 --> 00:15:10,740
Mom, don't be angry.

348
00:15:10,740 --> 00:15:11,570
We were just joking.

349
00:15:11,710 --> 00:15:12,140
Huan'er,

350
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:13,720
