351
00:15:13,950 --> 00:15:14,590
I don't want!

352
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:15,540
Come on, wear it on.

353
00:15:15,950 --> 00:15:16,620
So pretty!

354
00:15:16,740 --> 00:15:17,740
How beautiful!

355
00:15:18,780 --> 00:15:20,350
Look here. Ready?

356
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,350
I don't want!

357
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:22,110
Just take a look.

358
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:23,070
Just take a look.

359
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:24,900
One, two, three.

360
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:40,740
Sister,

361
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,020
after thinking about it,

362
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:45,350
I wish to change back
to the previous cake,

363
00:15:45,830 --> 00:15:46,590
