364
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:47,350
Sure!

365
00:16:05,380 --> 00:16:06,110
Lina,

366
00:16:06,350 --> 00:16:07,350
happy birthday!

367
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,740
This was specially chosen by my dad.

368
00:16:10,350 --> 00:16:11,380
This looks pretty nice.

369
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:13,070
Look.

370
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:14,680
Come on, let's celebrate the birthday.

371
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:16,780
