could you take it seriously?

372
00:16:16,780 --> 00:16:18,500
Wasn't it just a joke?

373
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,070
What joke?

374
00:16:19,070 --> 00:16:20,380
That was a scare, okay?

375
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:20,950
Fine, a scare.

376
00:16:20,950 --> 00:16:21,780
Sorry, sorry.

377
00:16:22,350 --> 00:16:24,190
Light the candles.

378
00:16:26,230 --> 00:16:31,780
Happy birthday to you.

379
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:34,950
Happy birthday to me.

380
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:37,990
Happy birthday to me.

381
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,040
Make a wish, make a wish.

382
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:40,380
Make a wish. Mom, make a wish.

383
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:44,710
Blow out the candles.

384
00:16:46,710 --> 00:16:47,230
Alright.

385
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:50,260
Mom.

386
00:16:50,260 --> 00:16:51,190
Look how nice it is.

387
00:16:51,230 --> 00:16:53,070
I prepared you

388
