389
00:16:54,590 --> 00:16:55,070
Look.

390
00:16:55,070 --> 00:16:56,120
This is the one I prepared.

391
00:16:56,140 --> 00:16:57,260
There's even a birthday gift!

392
00:16:57,990 --> 00:16:58,430
Mom,

393
00:16:58,780 --> 00:16:59,470
open it and see.

394
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:06,260
Inside this,

395
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:08,150
