396
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:09,940
You learned this from Jing Xichi, right?

397
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:10,740
No creativity.

398
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:12,630
Yeah.

399
00:17:12,820 --> 00:17:14,100
