more pictures of you both.

403
00:17:20,670 --> 00:17:21,740
Oh, you're mistaken.

404
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:24,180
Your mom used to have more
than a dozen photo albums.

405
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,710
