406
00:17:25,780 --> 00:17:26,500
It left only...

407
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:30,500
Happy birthday.

408
00:17:31,230 --> 00:17:32,500
Mom, do you like it?

409
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:34,160
- Does it look nice?
- How about this one?

410
00:17:34,180 --> 00:17:34,990
Isn't it nice?

411
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,740
Come on, let's eat cake.

412
00:17:36,990 --> 00:17:38,710
Don't just eat cake.

413
00:17:38,990 --> 00:17:39,990
I'll cook some noodles.

414
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:41,470
Let me do it.

415
00:17:41,470 --> 00:17:42,500
You don't have to do it.

416
00:17:42,630 --> 00:17:43,910
You just stay and cut the cake.

417
00:17:43,950 --> 00:17:45,190
Let me do it. I'll do it.

418
00:17:46,740 --> 00:17:47,990
(Just as I expected,)

419
00:17:48,820 --> 00:17:51,430
(my parents' argument this time)

420
00:17:51,630 --> 00:17:54,300
(ended without any danger.)

421
00:17:54,910 --> 00:17:56,390
(Now, I finally understand)

422
00:17:57,020 --> 00:17:59,950
(only when the love is deep enough)

423
00:18:00,430 --> 00:18:01,740
(can one argue)

424
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:03,060
(with such confidence.)

425
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:05,260
(That's their)

