00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:25,100
Close your eyes.

438
00:18:26,780 --> 00:18:27,580
Close your eyes.

439
00:18:30,560 --> 00:18:31,460
You already closed?

440
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:33,580
Don't open your eyes
unless I let you open.

441
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:34,430
Don't open your eyes.

442
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:35,480
You must not open your eyes.

443
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:38,260
