444
00:18:38,300 --> 00:18:38,780
No.

445
00:18:38,910 --> 00:18:40,060
No peeking! Close your eyes.

446
00:18:40,230 --> 00:18:40,820
I got it.

447
00:18:40,910 --> 00:18:41,540
No peeking.

448
00:18:46,150 --> 00:18:46,670
Chen Huan'er!

449
00:18:48,260 --> 00:18:49,100
No peeking!

450
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:51,340
