451
00:18:52,230 --> 00:18:53,230
I'm watching you.

452
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,280
Don't open your eyes yet.

453
00:18:54,300 --> 00:18:55,300
I'm still watching you.

454
00:18:55,340 --> 00:18:56,500
