455
00:18:56,580 --> 00:18:57,870
You'll find out soon.

456
00:18:57,990 --> 00:18:58,580
Stop talking.

457
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:01,100
Don't open your eyes.

458
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,460
Stretch out your hand.

459
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:09,540
Stretch out your hand.

460
00:19:12,360 --> 00:19:14,360
No peeking.
