461
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:14,990
Wait a while.

462
00:19:14,990 --> 00:19:15,870
I didn't peek.

463
00:19:15,870 --> 00:19:16,740
Don't open your eyes.

464
00:19:18,870 --> 00:19:20,100
What's that sound?

465
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:21,870
Open your eyes.

466
00:19:35,390 --> 00:19:35,820
This...

467
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:39,470
Didn't they say they
don't sell this cake in slices?

468
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:42,260
This is just a small problem
