to show your filial piety?

495
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:33,390
Am I right?

496
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,260
It's done packing.

497
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:37,990
Thank you.

498
00:20:38,870 --> 00:20:40,230
