513
00:21:32,870 --> 00:21:34,950
Who cares if it's your birthday or not?

514
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:36,640
I say it's your birthday, then it is.

515
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:38,500
Happy birthday.

516
00:21:39,870 --> 00:21:41,230
Don't cry.

517
00:21:42,260 --> 00:21:42,910
Close your eyes.

518
00:21:46,470 --> 00:21:47,190
Make a wish.

519
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:50,060
Make a wish.

520
00:21:50,060 --> 00:21:51,960
Blow out the candle after making a wish.

521
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:08,780
Thank you.

522
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:15,580
It must be very delicious.

523
00:22:16,910 --> 00:22:17,430
Eat it.

524
00:22:18,260 --> 00:22:19,630
