527
00:22:24,080 --> 00:22:24,920
Here, hold it.

528
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:26,230
Eat it.

529
00:22:33,390 --> 00:22:34,020
How is it?

530
00:22:34,860 --> 00:22:35,950
