538
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:46,150
Try it, it's really good.

539
00:22:47,230 --> 00:22:47,780
Is it good?

540
00:22:49,900 --> 00:22:50,820
It's really delicious!

541
00:22:50,820 --> 00:22:51,640
It's really yummy.

542
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,150
No wonder it's so expensive.

543
00:22:55,060 --> 00:22:56,020
Is this pricey?

544
00:22:56,870 --> 00:22:57,340
Not really.

545
00:22:57,740 --> 00:22:58,990
I got it covered. Eat up.

546
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,300
Then, take another bite.

547
00:23:17,870 --> 00:23:18,430
Mom,

548
00:23:18,710 --> 00:23:20,190
