00:23:38,990 --> 00:23:39,430
Look.

561
00:23:40,910 --> 00:23:41,540
Song Hang.

562
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:42,740
This is nice.

563
00:23:42,740 --> 00:23:43,920
Dad, come and have some.

564
00:23:54,580 --> 00:23:55,710
