00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:08,950
Huan'er.

652
00:30:08,950 --> 00:30:09,300
Dad!

653
00:30:09,910 --> 00:30:10,430
You're back.

654
00:30:10,430 --> 00:30:11,600
Did you get wet in the rain?

655
00:30:11,820 --> 00:30:12,460
Not really.

656
00:30:12,540 --> 00:30:13,820
Really? Your clothes are soaked.

657
00:30:13,820 --> 00:30:14,630
Go home and change.

658
00:30:14,630 --> 00:30:15,100
Uncle Chen.

659
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,060
Hello. Go home and get changed.

660
00:30:17,060 --> 00:30:17,780
Bye, Uncle Chen.

661
00:30:17,780 --> 00:30:18,660
Don't catch a cold.

662
00:30:30,910 --> 00:30:31,500
All tidied up?

663
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,460
The rain stopped.

664
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,430
Didn't I tell you to change?

665
00:30:35,470 --> 00:30:36,240
Aren't you cold?

666
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:37,680
It's fine, Dad. I didn't get too wet.

667
00:30:42,190 --> 00:30:42,670
Huan'er,

668
00:30:43,190 --> 00:30:44,540
I want to ask you something.

669
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,230
It's so late already.

670
00:30:47,300 --> 00:30:49,670
What were you doing
with that boy from the Jing family?

671
00:30:50,500 --> 00:30:52,150
He brought me something to eat.

672
00:30:52,630 --> 00:30:54,300
Dad, I tell you I have eaten so much.

673
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:56,020
I feel like my stomach
is going to explode.

674
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:57,740
I can't take it, Dad.

675
00:30:57,950 --> 00:30:59,150
I need to go to the washroom.

676
00:30:59,820 --> 00:31:03,060
Mom, are you done yet?

677
00:31:03,150 --> 00:31:04,300
Mom, faster!

678
00:31:04,540 --> 00:31:05,670
My stomach hurts.

679
00:31:07,020 --> 00:31:08,430
I can't hold it, Mom.

680
00:31:21,060 --> 00:31:21,780
Liqiang,

681
00:31:22,670 --> 00:31:23,820
bring a bed sheet.

682
00:31:25,710 --> 00:31:27,470
I washed one for you. It just dried.

683
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:29,720
There's definitely one over there.
No need to bring that.

684
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:30,780
Just listen to me.

685
00:31:31,060 --> 00:31:32,300
The bed sheets there

686
00:31:32,360 --> 00:31:34,660
are always worn out,
and not as good as the ones at home.

687
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:36,150
What if you have an allergic reaction?

688
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:36,710
Dad,

689
00:31:37,630 --> 00:31:38,710
where are you going?

690
00:31:38,780 --> 00:31:39,780
Going on an outstation.

691
00:31:39,950 --> 00:31:40,910
Nonsense.

692
00:31:41,390 --> 00:31:42,740
Your dad has been transferred.

693
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:44,540
How bad your department is.

694
00:31:44,630 --> 00:31:45,910
Just transferring

695
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:47,740
without prior notice. So sudden!

696
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:49,230
I don't even know what to pack now.

697
00:31:49,340 --> 00:31:50,670
You got transferred, Dad?

698
00:31:50,870 --> 00:31:51,740
To Tonglin.

699
00:31:52,190 --> 00:31:53,910
Uncle Yang who
is the deputy section chief

700
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:54,820
has been promoted.

701
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:56,390
They are sending me there.

702
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:59,160
If I do well, I might get promoted
to be the deputy section chief too.

703
00:32:01,390 --> 00:32:04,190
I heard the sports university
in Tonglin is quite good.

704
00:32:04,990 --> 00:32:06,100
I'm near to the place.

705
00:32:06,100 --> 00:32:07,640
Let me check it out for you first.

706
00:32:08,430 --> 00:32:09,020
Got it.

707
00:32:12,910 --> 00:32:13,580
Liqiang,

708
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,950
I told you to bring more sweaters,

709
00:32:14,950 --> 00:32:15,870
but you wouldn't.

710
00:32:17,340 --> 00:32:18,780
It's just a temporary report-in.

711
00:32:18,820 --> 00:32:20,190
No need to bring so much!

712
00:32:20,670 --> 00:32:21,990
You're always so stubborn with me.

713
00:32:22,020 --> 00:32:22,870
How stubborn you are.

714
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:28,100
Take care of your mom for me.

715
00:32:28,230 --> 00:32:28,950
Don't worry.

716
00:32:31,260 --> 00:32:32,580
I'm getting older now.

717
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:35,200
I won't be going out
to the field as much anymore.

718
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:36,390
Once you enter university,

719
00:32:37,390 --> 00:32:38,260
I'll transfer back.

720
00:32:38,260 --> 00:32:40,440
Then, I can spend more time
with you and your mom.

721
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:41,150
Oh,

722
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:42,670
about your soccer...

723
00:32:42,870 --> 00:32:43,670
I know.

724
00:32:43,820 --> 00:32:44,940
Keep doing it until the end.

725
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:46,580
I get to go now.

726
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:54,420
(Tianhe No.3 Central Hospital
Family Housing Compound)

727
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:55,820
You've grown taller.

728
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:57,780
Really?

729
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:59,220
You look like an adult now.

730
00:33:02,060 --> 00:33:02,580
I'm off.

731
00:33:05,540 --> 00:33:06,060
Bye.

732
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:14,430
Where is Uncle Jing going?

733
00:33:15,540 --> 00:33:17,430
My dad got temporarily
assigned out of town.

734
00:33:19,910 --> 00:33:21,100
When will he be back?

735
00:33:21,990 --> 00:33:22,500
Don't know.

736
00:33:24,140 --> 00:33:25,190
Where did you go?

737
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:27,580
Bought a set of practice questions.

738
00:33:28,910 --> 00:33:29,390
Let's go.

739
00:33:36,910 --> 00:33:37,990
(I used to think)

740
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:40,390
(I was the only one
who was afraid to ask)

741
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:42,820
(when Dad would come back.)

742
00:33:43,670 --> 00:33:44,430
(I guess)

743
00:33:44,910 --> 00:33:47,340
(it's not just fear of an answer
that feels too far away.)

744
00:33:50,990 --> 00:33:52,100
I'm home!

745
00:33:53,580 --> 00:33:54,540
Huan'er, you're back.

746
00:33:55,470 --> 00:33:56,100
Dad.

747
00:33:56,910 --> 00:33:57,340
Oh, right.

748
00:33:57,540 --> 00:33:59,500
Don't touch the kitchen door just yet.

749
00:33:59,580 --> 00:34:01,190
I just fixed it and put some oil on it.

750
00:34:01,820 --> 00:34:03,740
Why do you fix the door suddenly?

751
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:05,020
Whenever

752
00:34:05,020 --> 00:34:06,740
