will definitely wake her up.

756
00:34:12,660 --> 00:34:15,310
(It's also the fear that my dad
who cares for us a lot)

757
00:34:15,950 --> 00:34:16,830
(might get upset)

758
00:34:17,270 --> 00:34:18,700
(after hearing it.)

759
00:34:22,390 --> 00:34:23,540
I'm leaving tomorrow.

760
00:34:23,580 --> 00:34:25,100
So, I better get this done quickly.

761
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:25,950
Oh yeah,

762
00:34:26,830 --> 00:34:28,140
I bought you some oranges.

763
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:29,580
They're really sweet. Try it now.

764
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:30,180
I'll try it.

765
00:34:33,910 --> 00:34:34,620
It's so sweet.

766
00:34:34,660 --> 00:34:35,140
Really?

767
00:34:35,180 --> 00:34:35,960
Try one. Try one.

768
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:36,500
I'll have one.

769
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:37,140
Sweet or not?

770
00:34:38,270 --> 00:34:38,700
Sweet.

771
00:34:38,700 --> 00:34:39,540
It's sweeter than me.

772
00:34:39,830 --> 00:34:41,580
Nothing's sweeter than my big girl.

773
00:34:43,390 --> 00:34:44,700
Dad, you're sweating so much.

774
00:34:44,700 --> 00:34:45,430
It's fine.

775
00:34:46,780 --> 00:34:47,920
Let me wipe it off for you.

776
00:34:48,740 --> 00:34:49,910
I'm getting VIP treatment.

777
00:34:49,990 --> 00:34:51,470
I got a little helper while working.

778
00:34:51,870 --> 00:34:52,270
All done.

779
00:34:55,580 --> 00:34:56,660
Look, this is too loose.

780
00:34:59,140 --> 00:35:00,350
I already told Mom,

781
00:35:00,660 --> 00:35:03,350
