pack up your things anymore.

782
00:35:05,180 --> 00:35:07,020
It's okay, whatever is
convenient for you two.

783
00:35:08,950 --> 00:35:09,430
Dad.

784
00:35:10,220 --> 00:35:11,470
Let's take a photo together.

785
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,990
