786
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:15,830
Well, I'm an adult now.

787
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,020
I just want to keep a memory.

788
00:35:17,390 --> 00:35:17,990
Can we?

789
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:19,310
Sure, we'll take one later.

