812
00:37:22,350 --> 00:37:22,870
Xichi.

813
00:37:31,860 --> 00:37:32,910
I passed my physical test.

814
00:37:37,060 --> 00:37:37,870
Congratulations!

815
00:37:39,140 --> 00:37:40,660
