845
00:39:15,660 --> 00:39:16,560
Something on your mind?

846
00:39:17,140 --> 00:39:18,060
It's nothing.

847
00:39:18,060 --> 00:39:18,500
I'm just

848
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:21,350
hesitating whether

849
00:39:21,390 --> 00:39:22,660
I should

850
00:39:23,020 --> 00:39:23,540
ask you about

851
00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:25,390
a good tutoring school recommendation.

852
00:39:25,430 --> 00:39:26,660
Of course, I have.

853
00:39:26,750 --> 00:39:28,350
Any level, any price range, you name it.

854
00:39:28,350 --> 00:39:29,240
Feel free to ask me.

855
00:39:29,430 --> 00:39:30,020
What happens?

856
00:39:30,270 --> 00:39:32,270
Are you thinking
of getting Xichi a tutor?

857
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:35,830
It's just...

